des: Ignacio Alvarez grounds into a double play, second baseman Christian Koss to shortstop Yu Chang to first baseman Niko Kavadas.   Drew Lugbauer out at 2nd.    Ignacio Alvarez out at 1st.

Cal Conley flies out to right fielder Rob Refsnyder.
